Message.SourceString: The statue has no further secrets for you.
Message.LocalizedString: The statue has no further secrets for you.

Message.SourceString: Well now, that explains this great hunk o' stone, it's the head to a great ruddy weapon. Here, I think I know how to make it now.
Message.LocalizedString: Well now, that explains this great hunk o' stone, it's the head to a great ruddy weapon. Here, I think I know how to make it now.

Message.SourceString: Oh, what's that? You found something? Let me take a look at that blueprint for you.
Message.LocalizedString: Oh, what's that? You found something? Let me take a look at that blueprint for you.

Message.SourceString: Oh, hello again. I'm impressed you've made it all the way out here. Really coming into your own, eh?
Message.LocalizedString: Oh, hello again. I'm impressed you've made it all the way out here. Really coming into your own, eh?

Message.SourceString: Oh, hello again. I'm impressed you've made it all the way out here. Really coming into your own, eh?
Message.LocalizedString: Oh, hello again. I'm impressed you've made it all the way out here. Really coming into your own, eh?

Message.SourceString: You see that place over there? Ashien's Watch they calls it. Used to be a site of some battle or other.
Message.LocalizedString: You see that place over there? Ashien's Watch they calls it. Used to be a site of some battle or other.

Message.SourceString: You see that place over there? Ashien's Watch they calls it. Used to be a site of some battle or other.
Message.LocalizedString: You see that place over there? Ashien's Watch they calls it. Used to be a site of some battle or other.

Message.SourceString: It's the sort of place where dragonkin would have hoarded their more interesting stuff. Feels like the sort of thing they'd do.
Message.LocalizedString: It's the sort of place where dragonkin would have hoarded their more interesting stuff. Feels like the sort of thing they'd do.

Message.SourceString: I found a strange stone block covered in weird sigils, but then the garou ran me out of the place with threats of pointy sticks.
Message.LocalizedString: I found a strange stone block covered in weird sigils, but then the garou ran me out of the place with threats of pointy sticks.

Message.SourceString: I'm guessing you're much better at all this fighting malarky. Mind poking around? See what's sealed away?
Message.LocalizedString: I'm guessing you're much better at all this fighting malarky. Mind poking around? See what's sealed away?

Message.SourceString: A seal somewhere has broken.
Message.LocalizedString: A seal somewhere has broken.

Message.SourceString: The granite maul, now there's a weapon with heft. I wonder what other wonders the vaults are hiding?
Message.LocalizedString: The granite maul, now there's a weapon with heft. I wonder what other wonders the vaults are hiding?

Message.SourceString: Oh. You appear to be a little overburdened. I've got something for you, but you should come back to me when you have space to carry it.
Message.LocalizedString: Oh. You appear to be a little overburdened. I've got something for you, but you should come back to me when you have space to carry it.

Message.SourceString: The door is sealed by Dragonkin magic.
Message.LocalizedString: The door is sealed by Dragonkin magic.

Message.SourceString: You find a weapon blueprint written in dwarvish. Perhaps someone nearby can help translate it.
Message.LocalizedString: You find a weapon blueprint written in dwarvish. Perhaps someone nearby can help translate it.

Message.SourceString: You find a weapon blueprint written in dwarvish. Perhaps Doric can help translate it.
Message.LocalizedString: You find a weapon blueprint written in dwarvish. Perhaps Doric can help translate it.

Message.SourceString: How's the investigation going? I know Ashien's Watch must have something interesting to discover.
Message.LocalizedString: How's the investigation going? I know Ashien's Watch must have something interesting to discover.

Message.SourceString: These sorts of weapons are what an artisan lives for. Enjoy crafting it and then hitting your enemies with it.
Message.LocalizedString: These sorts of weapons are what an artisan lives for. Enjoy crafting it and then hitting your enemies with it.

Message.SourceString: Oh, you've already been in the vault? Brilliant, what did you find?
Message.LocalizedString: Oh, you've already been in the vault? Brilliant, what did you find?

Message.SourceString: Hrmm, this looks like a blueprint for a very special weapon, and look, I already found a bit to get you started!
Message.LocalizedString: Hrmm, this looks like a blueprint for a very special weapon, and look, I already found a bit to get you started!

Message.SourceString: Ah, enjoy making that. These sorts of weapons are what an artisan lives for.
Message.LocalizedString: Ah, enjoy making that. These sorts of weapons are what an artisan lives for.
